DEPENDENCIES
------------
Read docs/source/setup.rst to setup the environment.

RUNNING
-------
First edit the library directory (change line 3 of the .sp file) to match where
you installed the sky130 sdk.  Then run:

    ./run.sh

View the waveform:

    ./view.py


